<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
lang="en" metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
i18n:domain="plone">
<body>
<metal:content-core fill-slot="main">
<metal:content-core define-macro="main"
        tal:define="cview nocall:context/@@soercontent_view;">
    <div id="parent-title"  style="background:url(http://www.eea.europa.eu/draft.png);">
        <h1 id="parent-fieldname-title" class="documentFirstHeading">
            SOER 2015 — The European environment — state and outlook 2015
        </h1>

        <div class="documentDescription">Global, European and country-level assessment of the European environment
        </div>
    </div>
        <!--? SOER2015 Template-->
        <!--? Tabbed navigation -->
        <div class="top-highlights">
            <ul class="eea-tabs eea-tabs-soer">
                <li><a href="#tab-synthesis-report" id="tab-synthesis-report"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-clipboard eea-icon-2x"></span>Synthesis report</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-global-megatrends" id="tab-global-megatrends"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-globe eea-icon-2x"></span>Global megatrends</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-thematic-briefing" id="tab-thematic-briefing"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-flask eea-icon-2x"></span>European briefings</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-cross-country-comparisons" id="tab-cross-country-comparisons"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-bar-chart-o eea-icon-2x"></span>Cross-country comparisons</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-regions-countries" id="tab-regions-countries"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-map-marker eea-icon-2x"></span>Countries<br>and regions</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="eea-row">
                <div class="column-area">
                    <div class="eea-tabs-panels eea-tabs-panels-soer">
                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>SOER 2015 Synthesis provides a comprehensive overview of the key environmental challenges Europe is facing today, their links to the economy and the society, policy responses, and possible ways to facilitate long-term transition. It draws on all the other parts of SOER 2015.</p>
                            <div class="portalMessage" tal:condition="isAnon" style="font-size:150%;line-height:1.5em;">
                                  <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-magic"></span>
                                    The <a href="http://www.eea.europa.eu/soer/2015-pre-launch">upcoming new version (SOER 2015)</a> will be published on <strong>3 March 2015</strong><br>
                                    <a href="http://www.eea.europa.eu/soer/2015-pre-launch">Read more</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="eea-list-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('collections/synthesis', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                             </div>


                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right">
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="pdf-language-choice">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-language eea-icon-2x"></span>Here we display the list of Synthesis PDF in different languages.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="epub-language-choice">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-language eea-icon-2x"></span>Here we display the list of Synthesis Epub in different languages.
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <p class="pull-left">Download Synthesis report</p> <a class="download-pdf pull-left fancybox" href="#pdf-language-choice"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left fancybox" href="#epub-language-choice"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>These 11 global megatrends provide a backdrop for understanding the global forces at play affecting the environment in Europe in a longer-term and global context.</p>

                            <tal:global tal:define="results python:cview.content(parent_id='soer-2015', object_id='global')">
                                <ul>
                                    <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                        <a tal:attributes="href result/url">
                                            <span tal:content="result/title">Global</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </tal:global>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right"><p class="pull-left">Download all global megatrends</p> <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>European briefings present the state, recent trends and prospects in 25 key environmental themes, grouped in three clusters: environmental themes; socio-economic dimensions; and systemic perspectives.</p>


                            <tal:europe>
                                <div class="eea-list-columns eea-three-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('collections/environmental-themes', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <h4>Environmental themes</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                                </div>

                                <div class="eea-list-columns eea-three-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('collections/socio-economic-dimensions', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <h4>Socio-economic dimensions</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                                </div>

                                <div class="eea-list-columns eea-three-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('collections/systemic-perspectives', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <h4>Systemic perspectives</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                                </div>

                            </tal:europe>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right"><p class="pull-left">Download all European briefings</p> <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a></div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>Cross-country comparisons provide a deeper analysis around selected topics. They are based on EEA indicators covering a number of EEA countries.</p>

                            <tal:countries-comparison tal:define="results python:cview.content(parent_id='soer-2015', object_id='countries-comparison')">
                                <ul>
                                    <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                        <a tal:attributes="href result/url">
                                            <span tal:content="result/title">Countries Comparison</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </tal:countries-comparison>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right"><p class="pull-left">Download all cross-country comparisons</p> <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a></div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>Country briefings provide an overview of state of the environment across 39 European countries, based on national state-of-environment reports. Regional briefings address region-specific environmental issues affecting several EEA countries.</p>
                            <h4>Countries briefings</h4>
                            <div tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('collections/country-briefings', None);" tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog(batch=False)"
                                        tal:condition="results">
                                    <tal:countries tal:define="results_length python:len(results);
                                                               ratio python: (results_length + 6) / 3;
                                                               double_ratio python: ratio * 2;">
                                        <ul class='eea-list-columns eea-three-columns'>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result python:results[:ratio]">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul class='eea-list-columns eea-three-columns'>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result python:results[ratio:double_ratio]">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <div class='eea-list-columns eea-three-columns'>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li tal:repeat="result python:results[double_ratio:]">
                                                    <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                        <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                    </a>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>

                                            <div tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('collections/regional-briefings', None);"
                                                    tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                                <h4>Regional briefings</h4>
                                                <ul tal:define="res python:collection.queryCatalog()">
                                                    <li tal:repeat="result res">
                                                        <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                            <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                        </a>
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </tal:countries>
                                </tal:results>
                            </div>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right"><p class="pull-left">Download all countries and regions</p> <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left" href="#"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!--? eea-tabs-panels -->
                </div>
                <div class="right-column-area">
                    <dl class="portlet portletStaticText portlet-static-help">

                        <dt class="portletHeader">
                        <span class="portletTopLeft"></span>
                        <span>
                            SOER 2015 - EXPLORE
                        </span>
                        <span class="portletTopRight"></span>
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="portletItem odd">
                        <a class="fancybox" href="#popup-slideshare">
                           <img width="100%" height="200px" src="http://www.eea.europa.eu/soer-2015/soer-explore-image/image_preview">
                        </a>
                        <div style="display:none">
                            <div id="popup-slideshare">
                               <iframe src="//www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/28424044" width="595" height="485" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no" style="border:1px solid #CCC; border-width:1px; margin-bottom:5px; max-width: 100%;" allowfullscreen> </iframe>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- iframe width="100%" height="200px" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/dTp_I_7aN2c?vq=large" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" id="b1odf0i58fmngio2fgk77kh9e5hmjd"></iframe -->

                        </dd>
                        <dd class="portletItem odd">
                         Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
                        </dd>


                    </dl>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--? END Tabbed navigation -->
        <!--? Gallery & Navigation -->
        <div class="lower-highlights">
            <!--? Key facts -->
            <div class="eea-row">
                <div class="column-area">


            <div id="boxes">
		<div metal:define-macro="keyfacts-slider"
		    tal:define="background_img_path background_img_path| python: context.getCanonical().absolute_url() + '/image_large'  "
		     id="keyfacts-slider" class="figure keyFactsSlider">
                       <div class="keyfactsImgContainer"><img class="keyfacts-bgimg" src=""
                        tal:attributes="src background_img_path"  /></div>
                       <div id="boxes" tal:define="items context/soer2015_getAllKeyFacts">
                            <div id="soer-top-area">
                                <!-- all key facts and messages -->
                                <dl
                                    class="portlet slidePortlet" >
                                    <dt class="portletHeader" style="padding:5px;" i18n:translate="">Key messages</dt>
                                     <dd class="portletItem" style="left: 650px;" tal:repeat="item items">
                                       <span>
                                          <a href="" title="Read more of the key fact"
                                              class="moreLink link-plain" style="font-size:100%;"
                                              tal:attributes="href item/parent_url;title item/parent_title;"
                                              i18n:attributes="title"
                                              i18n:translate="" tal:content="item/parent_title">more</a>:&nbsp;
                                          <span tal:replace="structure item/text"></span>
                                          <a href="" title="Read more of the key fact"
                                              class="moreLink link-plain" style="font-size:100%;"
                                              tal:attributes="href item/parent_url;title item/parent_title;"
                                              i18n:attributes="title"
                                              i18n:translate="">See briefing</a>
                                        </span>
                                     </dd>
                                </dl>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
                </div> <!--? END Key facts -->

                <!--? Navigation portlet-->
                <div class="right-column-area">
                    <dl class="portlet portletNavigationTree">
                        <dt class="portletHeader" id="firstHeader">
                        <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015">SOER 2015 - The European environment -
                            State and Outlook</a>
                        </dt>
                        <dt class="portletSubMenuHeader">
                        <span class="title eea-icon-right-container">Menu</span>
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="portletItem lastItem">
                        <ul class="navTree navTreeLevel0">
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-global">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/about"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>About SOER</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-europe">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/for-journalists"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>For journalists</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-countries-comparison">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/events"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>Events</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-countries">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/feedback"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>Feedback</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-progress-monitoring">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/photos-and-videos"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>Photos and videos</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        </dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
                <div class="right-column-area pull-right">
                    <dl id="portlet-followus">
                        <dt class="portletHeader">Follow us</dt>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="twitter-link" title="Follow us on Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/euenvironment">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="facebook-link" title="Follow us on Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/European.Environment.Agency">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="youtube-link" title="Follow us on YouTube" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/EEAvideos">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="rss-link" title="Subscribe to RSS Feed" class="link-plain" tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/subscription/news-feeds">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="email-link" title="Subscribe by email" href="#subscribe-popup" class="fancybox">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--? END Gallery & Navigation -->

</metal:content-core>
</metal:content-core>
</body>
</html>
